        It's a battle plan for tackling what matters. <br> The second edition of Three Pipe Problems doesn't just ask you to think differently—it demands you act differently. Whether you lead a nonprofit, design products, pastor a church, or build a business, your problem-solving ability isn't just valuable — it's essential.
